But before the programme had even finished, hundreds of viewers had taken to social media to express their outrage.

Emma Togwell said: 'How disgusting is Judy finnigan she needs to be sacked.' 

A Twitter user called Dave said: 'Judy finnigan is a disgrace for her comments on Ched Evans. ITV should sack her immediately.'

